Neighborhood Map
=================================
This neighborhood map provides you with a map of the Waukesha, WI area with some markers pointing out points of interest.

Installation Instructions
=================================
1. Download the program from the GitHub repository here to a folder on your computer: https://github.com/jbrunette/udacity_neighborhood_map
2. Open the "index.html" file in the main folder.

Using the Program
=================================
Upon opening the index.html file, you'll be greeted with a map of the Waukesha, WI area, a list of points of interest and a search box.
Type something into the search box to filter the points of interest.
Click an item in the list on the left or one of the markers in the map to get more information about that location and
a link to yet more information.
